### KORAK 3: Astro Rendering (Website)

Imamo `sync-docs.js` koji kopira `README.md` u `website/src/content/docs/index.md`. Ali Astro treba layout da to prikaže.

**1. Instaliraj Astro Tailwind (ako već nisi):**
(Unutar `website/` foldera)
```bash
pnpm astro add tailwind
```

**2. Kreiraj Layout:** `website/src/layouts/Layout.astro`
```astro
---
interface Props {
	title: string;
}

const { title } = Astro.props;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="description" content="Valter ERP Documentation" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<title>{title}</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-200 font-sans">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
            <header class="mb-12 border-b border-slate-800 pb-6 flex justify-between items-center">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-400">VALTER ERP</h1>
                <nav class="space-x-4">
                    <a href="/" class="hover:text-white">Home</a>
                    <a href="/roadmap" class="hover:text-white">Roadmap</a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/Eris-Margeta/valter-25" class="hover:text-white">GitHub</a>
                </nav>
            </header>
			<slot />
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
```

**3. Kreiraj Dynamic Page za Dokumentaciju:** `website/src/pages/[...slug].astro`
Ovo je magija. Ovo će uhvatiti *sve* markdown fajlove koje je `sync-docs.js` kopirao i pretvoriti ih u HTML.

```astro
---
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

export async function getStaticPaths() {
  // Ovdje učitavamo 'docs' kolekciju koju puni tvoja sync skripta
  const blogEntries = await getCollection('docs');
  return blogEntries.map(entry => ({
    params: { slug: entry.slug }, props: { entry },
  }));
}

const { entry } = Astro.props;
const { Content } = await entry.render();
---

<Layout title={entry.data.title}>
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-emerald max-w-none">
        <h1>{entry.data.title}</h1>
        <Content />
    </article>
</Layout>
```

**4. Definiraj Kolekciju:** `website/src/content/config.ts`
```typescript
import { defineCollection, z } from 'astro:content';

const docsCollection = defineCollection({
  type: 'content',
  schema: z.object({
    title: z.string(),
    // Ostala polja su opcionalna
  }),
});

export const collections = {
  'docs': docsCollection,
};
```

---

### KORAK 4: Community Files

U rootu projekta:

**`CONTRIBUTING.md`**
```markdown
# Contributing to VALTER

Thank you for your interest in building the future of Data Operating Systems!

## Getting Started
1. Fork the repo.
2. Run `just dev` to start the Monorepo environment.
3. Make your changes in `core/` (Rust) or `dashboard/` (React).

## Pull Requests
- Please follow the existing code style.
- Ensure `cargo test` passes.
- Update documentation if you change configuration options.
```

---

### ZADATAK ZA TEBE

1.  **Kopiraj** ove YAML konfiguracije u `.github/workflows/`.
2.  **Postavi** Astro stranice kako je navedeno u Koraku 3.
3.  **Pushaj** sve na GitHub.
4.  **Testiraj Release:**
    *   Otiđi na GitHub -> Releases -> Draft a new release.
    *   Stavi tag `v0.1.0`.
    *   Klikni "Publish release".
    *   Gledaj "Actions" tab kako tvoji serveri rade i izbacuju binarne datoteke!

Nakon ovoga, Valter je **službeno živ** i spreman za distribuciju.
